message.text:
🌟The spotlight’s waiting for YOU! 🫵🏻 

After years of silence, the stage is ready…and this time, we’re coming back bigger and louder 🕺🏻

This is the FEU PSYawan comeback you’ve all been waiting for. Think you’ve got the moves to own the spotlight? Then it’s time to step up 🎶✨

Groove your way into the PSYawan and join us at September 15, 16, and 17. This is your chance to be part of the comeback everyone will be talking about.  💥

This is your moment. This is your stage. This is PSYawan 2025.

Scan the QR code below to fill out the pre-enlistment form and show us your groove!
